  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"1.3.0-alpha05\" data-text=\"Version 1.3.0-alpha05\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 1.3.0-alpha05</h3>\n<p>September 6, 2023</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.wear.compose:compose-*:1.3.0-alpha05</code> is released. <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/3315f1ef094c312203fe26841287902916fbedf5..9ce75ea1baa2af10dda8f787f69c40c6654bcac1/wear/compose\">Version 1.3.0-alpha05 contains these commits.</a></p>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>We have added handling in Swipe to Reveal so that only one item at a time can be swiped. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I3cd7a5692830ddde9142c11d58c067790fd836ab\">I3cd7a</a>)</li>\n<li>Improved the documentation of <code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">ScalingLazyColumnDefaults</code> to better match its actual behavior. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/I886d362cce1f4c909e27d84b1f2bfc855daae83d\">I886d3</a>)</li>\n</ul>",
